mp-units Integration Guide
===========================

[mp-units](https://mpusz.github.io/mp-units/latest/) is a header-only library providing compile-time dimensional analysis
and type-safe unit conversions for C++20 and later.

Requirements:

- C++20 or later

CMake Integration
-----------------

In your project's CMakeLists.txt:

    set(CMAKE_CXX_STANDARD 20)
    set(CMAKE_CXX_STANDARD_REQUIRED ON)
    
    # On Windows with MSVC, MSVC 2022 is required
    if(MSVC AND MSVC_VERSION LESS 1940)
        message(FATAL_ERROR "mp-units requires MSVC 2022 or later")
    endif()
    
    find_package(mp-units REQUIRED CONFIG)    
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE mp-units::mp-units)
